### Test Metadata Endpoints for Developer Help

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5214/api

### Get Available Document Types
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/metadata/document-types
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Available Document Statuses
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/metadata/statuses
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Search Fields Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/metadata/search-fields
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Search Examples
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/metadata/search-examples
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Document Model Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/metadata/document-model
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Simple Search (using metadata info)
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents?documentType=Legal Contract&status=Active&maxResults=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Advanced Search (using examples)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "SearchMethod": "DocumentTypeAndDateRange",
  "DocumentType": "Contract",
  "DateStoredFrom": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "DateStoredTo": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "Status": "Active",
  "MaxResults": 25
}

###